welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Plant City, where southern charm and hospitality await you! Known as the "Winter Strawberry Capital of the World," we invite you to explore our quaint town and savor its sweet offerings."

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Municipal Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Municipal Airport handles all freight and cargo operations.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Zephyrhills Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Zephyrhills Airport caters to private and charter flights.

wifi.note: WiFi is available throughout the airport for free.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Bartow Airport serves all commercial flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Mac Dill AFB Airport serves both commercial and military flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Peter O'Knight Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Peter O'Knight Airport caters to private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Tampa International Airport serves all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Airside A
terminals.description: Airside A at Tampa International Airport serves mainly domestic flights for airlines such as Delta, Southwest, and United.

terminals.name: Airside C
terminals.description: Airside C at Tampa International Airport serves mainly international flights for airlines such as Air Canada, British Airways, and Lufthansa.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport. Premium WiFi is also available for purchase.
